{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Trivia Deal is the first ever trivia roguelike game, blending the brain-teasing fun of trivia with the addictive strategy and endless replayability of roguelikes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Randomised trivia deck</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each run is a new challenge, battle your way through each column and maximise your score by getting consecutive answers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820760/extras/TD-Deckload.gif?t=1737064500\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Earn tokens</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Answer questions of varying difficulty correct to earn tokens and clear columns, the more difficult the question, the more tokens you earn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820760/extras/TD-Correct.gif?t=1737064500\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Purchase abilities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Purchase strategic abilities such as the 50/50, slow timer, 2x token.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820760/extras/TD-Ability.gif?t=1737064500\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Avoid mistakes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Answering incorrectly will penalise you by locking that column, forcing you to spend 5 tokens to unlock with the key ability.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820760/extras/TD-Incorrect.gif?t=1737064500\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Win the game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete all columns to win the game, and try to beat your high score.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820760/extras/TD-WinGame.gif?t=1737064500\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_t